dc_description_s: REMOTE DOWNLOAD NOT AVAILABLE - please contact data@library.columbia.edu for access. Zhejiang China Province Boundary, 2000 is a polygon theme representing the boundaries of Zhejiang Province for 2000.  This data layer is part of the China 2000 Township Census data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
